<div class="col-sm-12 no-padding botMARG">
    <h1 class="contentPageH1">INTRO - DEVELOPMENTAL DISABILITIES & SERVICES<small class="contentH1-small">&nbsp;CERTIFICATE</small></h1>
    <ol class="breadcrumb">
        <li class="contentp">@Html.ActionLink("Home", "Index", "Home")</li>
        <li class="contentp">@Html.ActionLink("All Certificates", "AllCertificates", "Certificates")</li>
        <li class="active contentp">Intro - Developmental Disabilities & Services</li>
    </ol>
    <img class="img-responsive" width="100%" src="~/Content/images/cert-developmentaldisabilities.jpg" alt="three medical professionals behind a computer" />

</div>

<div class="col-sm-8 mid-padding">


    <h1 class="contentH1">Workshop Objective</h1><hr class="hrp" />


    <p class="contentp">
        This course is designed as a general introduction for the public to the Developmental Services field.

        Students will develop basic knowledge on topics that include but are not limited to:
    </p>

    <ul class="contentp">
        <li>Autism Spectrum Disorder</li>

        <li>Fetal Alcohol Spectrum Disorder</li>

        <li>Down Syndrome</li>

        <li>Speech/Language Disorders</li>

        <li>Mental Health issues / Dual Diagnosis</li>

        <li>Physical disabilities</li>

        <li>Behavioural Support & Facilitation Techniques</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="contentp">
        The knowledge students receive over this course is strictly for personal use however students who

        complete this course and then join our full Developmental Service Worker Diploma program will be

        given a tuition credit. (*Note: students must also meet all DSW program course prerequisites for

        admission to the full program)
    </p>
    <br />


    <h1 class="contentH1">Course Prerequisite</h1><hr class="hrp" />
    <ul class="contentp">
        <li>English Proficiency</li>

        <li>To succeed in this course, learners should exhibit emotional maturity, strong interpersonal skills, and a commitment to integration</li>
    </ul>
    <br />


    <h1 class="contentH1">Course Duration and Schedule</h1><hr class="hrp" />

    <p class="contentp">
        5 Saturdays: 9:00am-5:00pm
    </p>
    <br />


    <h1 class="contentH1">Tuition</h1><hr class="hrp" />
    <ul class="contentp">
        <li>
            $399.00 CAD + $100.00 CAD books (or $299.00 CAD + books if you are a current Medix student)
            <ul>
                <li>40-hour training session</li>
                <li>Course training materials</li>
                <li>Certificate of completion</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
    </ul>

    <br />
    <p class="contentp">
        This program does not require approval under the Private Career Colleges Act, 2005.

    </p>

    <br />
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-lg btn-block contentH2"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-send"></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;@Html.ActionLink("GO TO CERTIFICATES DIRECTORY", "AllCertificates", "Certificates")</button>
    <br />
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-lg btn-block contentH2"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-map-marker"></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;@Html.ActionLink("GO TO CAMPUS DIRECTORY", "Index", "Campuses")</button>

    <br />
</div>

